HEADWORD: Exciter
<hw>Ex*cit"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, excites.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Hope is the grand <qex>exciter</qex> of industry.</q> <rj><qau>Dr.
